OL,3,CWelsh Labour politician Hefin David
OL,4,Cdied by suicide, coroner rules
OL,6,FWelsh Labour politician Hefin David
OL,7,Fdied by suicide, a coroner has ruled.
OL,9,FMr David, 47, who had served as member
OL,10,Fof the Welsh Parliament for Caerphilly
OL,11,Fsince 2016, was found dead at his home
OL,12,Fon August 12, 2025.
OL,14,FIn a record of inquest, senior coroner
OL,15,FCaroline Saunders concluded Mr David's
OL,16,Fdeath was a suicide.
OL,18,FAn inquest opening at Gwent Coroner's
OL,19,FCourt previously heard Mr David was
OL,20,Fidentified at the scene by his sister.
