OL,6,FHe would have turned 48 the next day.
OL,8,FSpeaking in the Senedd following Mr
OL,9,FDavid's death, First Minister Eluned
OL,10,FMorgan described him as a "truly
OL,11,Fremarkable human being".
OL,13,FShe said Mr David had a "heart that
OL,14,Floved fiercely" and expressed sympathy
OL,15,Ffor his partner Vikki Howells, the
OL,16,FCynon Valley MS and minister for
OL,17,Ffurther and higher education in the
OL,18,FWelsh Government.
